title: I’m a Human, but More of a Vampire
description: I’m a Human, but More of a Vampire Because of the advent of a mysterious “teeth”, the selected “human vampire” was born. He killed his biological mother by mistake and was beheaded by his father who was the sanctioner. When everything seemed to end, the cold and deserted world nightmare had just begun… Human but Vampire I’m a Human, but More of a Vampire I’m Human, I’m Vampire 我是人类，更是吸血鬼
